{"tid":246033,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得上一輩識social多啲","createTime":"2017-05-16T16:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T06:45:49.000Z","uid":83913,"like":51,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"717114832f43748fc0e9105070a9d09ffd80900d","tid":246033,"uid":83913,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"上一輩，講緊四十歲以上果d<br />\n<br />\n就算講d野你未必啱聽，可能好煩<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋總係唔會冷場dead air<br />\n<br />\n好多仲要轉數好快，<br />\n<br />\n好識讚人(雖然多數係假，唔係真心)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但比起呢一代(唔係特登踩)<br />\n<br />\n但自己有時出到去社交場合，真係一句野都講唔到。<br />\n<br />\n又接唔到人哋d話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ceb35bc7225a6c027edce87211d4c852c356c5","tid":246033,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"雖然老果輩有時講野懶係風趣，<br />\n<br />\n但無可否認佢哋講完果d唔好笑既gag之後，<br />\n<br />\n個氣氛係真係輕鬆咗<br />\n<br />\n佢哋亦都唔係覺得自己講得好少，<br />\n<br />\n但係一種社交必要講既說話"},{"pid":"4953a7697cdf4edfa7abed7e04058ea4c5018f12","tid":246033,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"好似冇乜毒撚<br />\n定毒個d已經生存唔到/ 摺埋/ 死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b87bdbb276f9cc13f8bf8ba689ee5ec2d4bf05","tid":246033,"uid":89065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:31:47.000Z","msg":"覺 因為食鹽多過你食米<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b828bcf6f3454bf16de320e1671f43823ed0ea7","tid":246033,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c7a2c5480f8dc824f1a8c1f9be52d942d3543c1","tid":246033,"uid":83913,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"其實好多時我哋心入面屌緊老一輩講野無聊、無深度、唔好笑。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋唔係唔知自己講既話題無深度，<br />\n<br />\n而係佢哋知道係某d場合、同某d人，只能夠講某種說話，講到某種深度，點到即止<br />\n<br />\n佢哋皮笑肉不笑，此乃最高境界"},{"pid":"3d93ab120062788a25c67918dcac6303