/>\n我同個吹氣公仔食飯好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9ad7469096ae1d509b8c7b45c1d1fcb616bcad","tid":246033,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:43:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b452bb1866b87ee4112191c1a47ba8b8fb79eab0","tid":246033,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我覺得佢地係真on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇咩行業同埋咩聚會啦。<br />\n<br />\n如果普通親戚食飯果d就真on9既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45eb1672e30f57fb498449be2b81c706ef48e9fa","tid":246033,"uid":93266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:51:47.000Z","msg":"以前無咁多通訊軟件...<br />\n<br />\n正常人既社交力係高少少既..."},{"pid":"9edc4935c022ac7701e79d57c88167ca496a46f6","tid":246033,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"香港應該復辟 刷鞋 卸膊 厚顏 無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e17bce1cdd03766cdd672a98f122510873eea00","tid":246033,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:09:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港應該復辟 刷鞋 卸膊 厚顏 無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打，事情又一定要咁極端既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54d2bfd2162b3700381559d57e7602cddad40d0","tid":246033,"uid":14214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:35:50.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申毒撚</span></span>"},{"pid":"ed4c795481581cb193e9bb09f26c78f5a400ceee","tid":246033,"uid":92017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20